query:
SELECT tp.id, tp.userId, tp.approvalStatus, tp.createdAt, u.email, u.name, u.role
FROM tutor_profiles tp
INNER JOIN users u ON tp.userId = u.id
WHERE tp.approvalStatus = 'pending'
ORDER BY tp.createdAt DESC;
